{
    "name": "Air Scamp",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Air Scamp",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "A pale blue head and paper-thin wings peek out from the cloud that clings to the air scamp. Air scamps are short-sighted and flighty, even relative to their kin; they are as likely to fly recklessly into battle as they are to whine in terror at a loud noise.",
